Pip3 install:

wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/pip/3.6/get-pip.py
--2025-01-31 10:00:57--  https://bootstrap.pypa.io/pip/3.6/get-pip.py

sudo python3 get-pip.py

VScode install:
wget https://update.code.visualstudio.com/1.84.0/linux-deb-arm64/stable -O code_arm64.deb

sudo dpkg -i code_arm64.deb

Python3 dev:
sudo apt install python3-dev
sudo apt install python3.6-dev  # Specifically for your Python version


I2C dependencies:
sudo apt install -y python3-smbus
sudo apt install -y i2c-tools

arduino stuff:
pip3 install adafruit-circuitpython-servokit
pip3 install Adafruit-Blinka
pip3 install approxeng.input
pip3 install evdev
pip3 install approxeng.input

